title: Jackie Christie Interview,Exclusive Interview with Ta'Kari Lee and more
itunes:title: Jackie Christie Interview,Exclusive Interview with Ta'Kari Lee and more
description:
Today on the show we had the most hated member on the show “Basketball Wives” Jackie Christie come by where she spoke about the drama between her and her daughter Ta’ Kari Lee, the beef between her and Shaunie O’Neal and more. Moreover the interview caused so much controversy that we were able to get a hold of her daughter Ta’Kari Lee for her to tell her side of the story between her and her mother, but who is telling the truth? Also, Charlamagne gave “Donkey of the Day” to three people that are now in the sunken place, former Raiders player Tim Brown, former Green Bay Packers Jermichael Finley and commentator Parrish Dennard for not seeing the injustice in America.
